00:00:09.120 --> 00:00:12.360
Where are we in 2024, and what's going to happen?

00:00:12.360 --> 00:00:14.200
What's the prophetic pulse?

00:00:14.200 --> 00:00:20.863
I'm a prophetic intercessor; the Lord shows me things that are coming and says, 'I need you to pray this way.

00:00:20.863 --> 00:00:23.298
I need you to pray for this or that.

00:00:23.298 --> 00:00:29.060
' This is basically what He has given me in the last couple of days.

00:00:29.430 --> 00:00:34.309
