00:01:09.040 --> 00:01:12.745
I'm going to talk about the economy first.

00:01:13.715 --> 00:01:20.479
I could talk about Joe Biden, and I think we will.

00:01:21.523 --> 00:01:34.279
I was taken up in the Spirit and saw January, then I was shown December where we are now, and the next couple of weeks.

00:01:34.719 --> 00:01:38.129
The Lord showed me it went into January.

00:01:38.431 --> 00:01:53.560
I saw Joe Biden and, you know how when you have no signal on a TV—when it's not plugged into an antenna or cable and you flip the channels—it's grainy?

00:01:54.580 --> 00:01:57.329
You see the static and there's no reception.

00:02:02.896 --> 00:02:06.782
That's how it was around Joe Biden's mind.

00:02:07.268 --> 00:02:12.951
That may sound funny, and I'm not making a joke; this is really what I saw when I was praying.

00:02:12.951 --> 00:02:16.170
I saw confusion.

00:02:16.540 --> 00:02:22.755
He was staring off in an even greater state of confusion than he has been.

00:02:22.755 --> 00:02:31.760
It's like it had escalated to another level in his mental capacity to handle things.

00:02:32.600 --> 00:02:38.480
I was praying over this, and it was like static electricity when you're flipping channels.

00:02:44.411 --> 00:02:55.780
Then I saw his son, Hunter, and there was an unveiling of things.

00:02:55.780 --> 00:03:07.900
I saw an exposing, like a ripping off of sheets, uncovering hidden things that were not supposed to be seen.

00:03:10.731 --> 00:03:35.159
This is what's really interesting: I was taken up into the third heaven and could see the devil manipulating things like a puppet master through the spirit realm over financial sectors and politics.

00:03:35.563 --> 00:03:47.416
The root is what we're after to destroy the fruit, but the fruit is what we're seeing behind closed doors.

00:03:51.142 --> 00:03:54.834
There was perversion over this financial corruption and some other things that were darker.

00:03:54.834 --> 00:04:06.783
Everyone was able to see the surface, but they weren't able to see the root.

00:04:21.900 --> 00:04:27.000
I saw the root was the devil.

00:04:31.250 --> 00:04:41.703
Hidden things were being revealed and exposed at a deeper level at the beginning of 2024.

00:04:41.703 --> 00:04:52.914
These things were even tied to Joe, and I saw it going back into the Obama administration.

00:04:58.951 --> 00:05:01.160
It was attached to the Obama administration somehow and went forward.

00:05:01.160 --> 00:05:02.289
That's what I was praying over.

00:05:02.578 --> 00:05:19.525
Then, all of a sudden, I was praying over the BRICS nations and what was coming in January regarding a new currency and a new petrodollar.

00:05:32.987 --> 00:05:33.511
I saw the United States had a plan to combat what was coming because they knew about it.

00:05:33.511 --> 00:05:37.973
America wasn't caught off guard.

00:05:49.813 --> 00:05:50.169
I saw Jerome Powell; he was sweating, and drops of sweat were coming down like he was nervous and worried.

00:06:11.940 --> 00:06:12.765
All of a sudden, I saw this massive, transparent latex balloon.

00:06:16.508 --> 00:06:21.830
There was housing, huge skyscrapers, trees, and the American economy all on this big balloon.

00:06:22.220 --> 00:06:29.776
He went to put the balloon to his lips to blow it up and make the economy bigger.

00:06:31.885 --> 00:06:36.180
He blew inflation into it.

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:44.460
When he blew it in, he was lowering interest rates.

00:06:45.186 --> 00:06:49.919
I saw interest rates being lowered in the springtime—possibly March.

00:06:52.730 --> 00:07:01.980
I'm not exactly sure what month it is, as I see various months and calendars, but I saw a springtime event coming.

00:07:02.693 --> 00:07:10.668
He breathed into it and kept saying to himself, 'Is this going to work?

00:07:14.950 --> 00:07:16.304
What is going to happen?

00:07:16.304 --> 00:07:17.840
' He was worried.

00:07:27.857 --> 00:07:28.240
All of a sudden, I saw him breathe into it, and the balloon started to expand.

00:07:28.240 --> 00:07:30.870
Inflation started expanding more and more.

00:07:30.870 --> 00:07:41.420
It was transparent, and all of a sudden, the balloon started to shake.

00:07:41.420 --> 00:07:46.319
There wasn't a lot of turmoil at this time.

00:07:55.404 --> 00:07:55.759
Then I heard the people at the Fed—the government entities over the finances—saying, 'It worked.

00:07:55.759 --> 00:07:56.959
Nothing happened.

00:08:03.695 --> 00:08:04.180
It wasn't that bad.

00:08:04.180 --> 00:08:17.039
' They waited a span of time, and then I saw into May and June, the summer months.

00:08:17.039 --> 00:08:24.426
They said, 'Let's do it again,' and breathed into the balloon again.

00:08:24.426 --> 00:08:29.200
It expanded even more, getting super big.

00:08:29.200 --> 00:08:33.868
Sweat was dripping off his face.

00:08:33.868 --> 00:08:41.800
Now the houses on top of this transparent balloon started to shake.

00:08:51.300 --> 00:08:58.073
The houses were trembling because the balloon was trembling.

00:08:58.073 --> 00:09:04.925
As the balloon got bigger, the foundation started to shake.

00:09:08.947 --> 00:09:11.280
It wasn't affecting the big buildings as much, but the whole balloon was trembling.

00:09:21.830 --> 00:09:34.079
He was breathing into this balloon, and his facial expressions showed he was nervous because he knew that balloon was about to pop and there was nothing he could do to stop it.

00:09:38.731 --> 00:09:45.063
They waited a little bit longer; I could see into June, July, and August.

00:09:52.880 --> 00:10:03.269
In September and October, I saw the balloon pop; it wasn't there anymore.

00:10:05.189 --> 00:10:10.020
I heard the word 'quantitative easing.

00:10:10.020 --> 00:10:17.519
' I'm not an economics person; I barely have a high school education.

00:10:17.519 --> 00:10:20.620
I'm just telling you what I see and hear in the spirit realm when I'm praying.

00:10:22.786 --> 00:10:26.320
