00:10:41.275 --> 00:10:41.523
Then I saw October, and things were different leading into the election.

00:10:41.772 --> 00:10:45.390
I won't get into that part yet.

00:10:45.390 --> 00:10:53.920
Remember I told you about the holly berries?

00:11:01.577 --> 00:11:04.506
I saw the green leaf and the red berries, and it flashed before me in the vision.

00:11:11.592 --> 00:11:12.240
The Lord said, 'Remember.

00:11:12.240 --> 00:11:23.474
' I saw a great economic crash, a major crash in the winter months of 2024 leading into 2025.

00:11:41.048 --> 00:11:43.176
It was very dark.

00:11:43.708 --> 00:11:50.760
I saw a great black depression.

00:11:50.760 --> 00:11:59.480
It felt like a heaviness in the spirit realm, a very heavy presence.

00:12:00.828 --> 00:12:08.516
