00:13:14.130 --> 00:13:20.104
They had a new dollar-type currency.

00:13:21.500 --> 00:13:34.781
There were still borders—America was America, Mexico was Mexico, and Canada was Canada—but they had a currency they used as a partnership, like the Euro.

00:13:45.639 --> 00:13:45.946
Thank you, Braden.

00:13:48.399 --> 00:13:50.290
It was like an American version of the Euro.

00:13:55.404 --> 00:13:57.030
They tried to salvage it.

00:13:58.000 --> 00:14:03.744
The person over America tried to build America back and salvage it through a Solomon-type anointing.

00:14:03.744 --> 00:14:10.006
I saw a Solomon-like endowment of wisdom from the Father.

00:14:10.006 --> 00:14:35.455
It was like taking pieces of a destroyed rocket ship, and the Mastermind behind it—the brilliance of the Lord Jesus Christ—downloaded into a human mind how to build it back.

00:14:50.419 --> 00:14:50.989
I saw this person building it back into something else, and the Lord said, 'America will never be what it was before.

00:14:50.989 --> 00:14:57.017
' But it will be something new; it will be something different.

00:15:07.660 --> 00:15:07.984
But those days that were before are over.

00:15:18.520 --> 00:15:21.918
He said it will never be...

00:15:25.302 --> 00:15:34.711
