00:15:42.119 --> 00:15:47.319
That part of it was destroyed; that thing being the top dog was over.

00:15:47.319 --> 00:15:52.579
Being the top dog of the world's economy was over.

00:15:52.579 --> 00:15:57.313
It was like you were just maintaining and keeping afloat.

00:15:57.313 --> 00:15:58.639
Does that make sense?

00:15:58.875 --> 00:16:00.288
I guess that's what...

