00:18:36.311 --> 00:18:38.940
It was a complete explosion; it was a complete meltdown of what we called...

00:18:40.460 --> 00:18:41.072
it was already broken; it was never fixed.

00:18:41.072 --> 00:18:50.305
With the raising of interest rates, there's nothing they could do, so it's like, 'Well, just throw it in the air and let it burn.

00:18:50.305 --> 00:18:53.520
' I'm trying to tell you all.

00:18:53.520 --> 00:19:05.119
And so when it went into it, they tried to make it look good for the election, but after that was over, it was complete.

00:19:05.119 --> 00:19:08.599
I'm going to pray for you all right now.

00:19:08.599 --> 00:19:17.520
